transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello, Sakshi ji?
Customer: Haan ji sir.
Executive: Haan, Ronak baat kar raha hu. Mujhe ek image change karni thi. Jo mere ye infrastructure wale mein jo images hai na.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Aur about us mein. Wo wo mere ghar ki images hai. To uski jagah pe maine jo last WhatsApp message kiya hai na image ka, wo mujhe change karna hai.
Customer: WhatsApp message matlab aapne kaha WhatsApp kiya hai?
Customer: IndiaMART pe. IndiaMART ka jo wo.
Executive: Haan, IndiaMART ka jo WhatsApp.
Customer: Aap mere number pe kar dete, okay, main. Okay.
Customer: Theek hai, ye number pe WhatsApp kar du main?
Executive: Haan, nahi is number pe nahi. Main hi karke message kar rahi hu aapke ghar. Kyuki mera number hai aap us pe kar do.
Customer: Theek hai, main kar deta hu us pe. Okay.
Executive: Okay.
summary:
Concerns:

- Wants to change images in infrastructure section.

- Images in 'About Us' section are of his house.



Resolution:

- Executive asked to send image on her WhatsApp number.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will send image on executive's WhatsApp number.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- image change, whatsapp, infrastructure, about us
